iv><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2e9 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">认识了心的本来面目，<span class="_ _6"></span>此时就如同站在最高的山巅上一览众</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2ea ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls26 ws0">山小般，其他任何法都不在话下。<span class="_ _a"></span><span class="ls22">”所以，此法对当前的人</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2eb ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">来讲，<span class="_ _8"></span>确实相当适合。<span class="_ _8"></span>藏地著名大德噶托度达也说过，<span class="_ _8"></span>末法</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2ec ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">时代五浊黑暗越厉害，<span class="_ _9"></span>大圆满加持的日光就越明亮、<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="lsa">越炽盛。</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2ed ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">因此，现在的众生很需要殊胜密法，尤其是大圆满的窍诀。<span class="_ _6"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x5e h21 y2ee ff15 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls54 ws0">（八） <span class="_ _1c"> </span><span class="ff16 ls0">问<span class="ffb fs3 ls55">：我是北大哲学系毕业的博士，现今在读</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h18 y1d2 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">博士后。<span class="_ _8"></span>我想请教堪布一个问题：<span class="_ _8"></span>我们无论做任何事，<span class="_ _8"></span>在某</div><div class="t m0 x9 h18 y2ef ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">些方面都很相似，<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="ls13">不管做生意还是盖寺院，<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="ls16">都需要聚合资源、</span></span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
